my dedication to the game,

255
00:13:28,390 --> 00:13:29,934
led to all this other stuff.

256
00:13:30,017 --> 00:13:33,395
Believe me, if I was averaging two points,
three rebounds,

257
00:13:33,479 --> 00:13:36,023
