316
00:17:25,335 --> 00:17:28,505
<i>Good evening,
basketball fans, wherever you may be.</i>

317
00:17:28,589 --> 00:17:33,427
<i>Tonight begins the 1992 NBA Finals.</i>

318
00:17:35,095 --> 00:17:37,532
<i>The Chicago Bulls,
