341
00:18:45,207 --> 00:18:47,918
<i>That's his fourth three-point field goal.</i>

342
00:18:48,502 --> 00:18:53,882
<i>Michael Jordan, with four three-pointers
in a half, has tied the NBA Finals record.</i>

343
00:18:53,966 --> 00:18:58,345
Michael didn't want anybody
to have nothing over him.

344
00:18:58,428 --> 00:19:01,014
<i>Jordan for three! Yes!</i>

345
00:19:02,141 --> 00:19:07,813
<i>An NBA Finals record.
Five three-pointers in a half.</i>

346
00:19:07,896 --> 00:19:12,025
And every time he hit a three,
he glanced over at me, at the NBC table.

347
00:19:12,609 --> 00:19:15,404
<i>Here's Jordan again
from downtown.</i>

348
00:19:17,030 --> 00:19:21,243
<i>Did you see that look?
Michael indicating he can't believe it.</i>

349
00:19:23,370 --> 00:19:29,293
