- Hey, partner. How you doing?
- How you doing?

844
00:48:10,429 --> 00:48:12,556
Haven't seen you since the photo shit.

845
00:48:12,639 --> 00:48:14,850
These are a couple
of your good fans right here.

846
00:48:14,933 --> 00:48:17,412
- Every day we come in to watch the game...
- Nice to meet you.

847
00:48:17,436 --> 00:48:18,913
...they're watching your show.

848
00:48:18,937 --> 00:48:21,398
Sooner or later,
you gotta get tired of <i>Seinfeld.</i>

849
00:48:21,481 --> 00:48:22,733
Let's go, guys.

850
00:48:23,901 --> 00:48:25,736
- Hi, Phil.
- How are you doing?

851
00:48:25,819 --> 00:48:26,945
All right, have a good game.

852
00:48:27,029 --> 00:48:29,281
- Principal's kicking you out.
- Good to see you.

853
00:48:29,364 --> 00:48:30,699
I'll see you, Jerry.

854
00:48:31,992 --> 00:48:32,826
All right...

855
00:48:32,910 --> 00:48:36,330
This is not gonna work, by the way.
I would get that out of there.

856
00:48:37,539 --> 00:48:38,899
- How you doing?
- All right.

857
00:48:38,957 --> 00:48:39,875
Have a good game.

858
00:48:39,958 --> 00:48:43,629
<i>When you get to the top,
it's great to be admired and respected.</i>

859
00:48:43,712 --> 00:48:45,923
<i>I'm not saying that wasn't fun.</i>

860
00:48:47,174 --> 00:48:49,134
<i>But every time I would get by myself,</i>

861
00:48:49,217 --> 00:48:52,596
<i>I'd think about the end of the season
and the ultimate goal,</i>

862
00:48:52,679 --> 00:48:54,640
<i>holding up that championship trophy</i>

863
00:48:54,723 --> 00:48:57,476
<i>and being recognized
as the best team in the world.</i>

864
00:48:58,060 --> 00:49:00,771
<i>It's something at the end
of this rainbow that I'm fighting for</i>

865
00:49:00,854 --> 00:49:03,440
<i>and I'm going to give
every little bit to get to it.</i>

